  "description": "A stunning nighttime landscape featuring a vibrant, star-filled sky above rolling hills. The sky is a deep, rich blue, densely populated with stars and what appears to be a faint streak of a shooting star or satellite. The hills are a warm, earthy brown, creating a strong contrast with the cool tones of the sky. A patch of green and golden foliage is visible in the lower right corner, adding depth and texture to the foreground. The overall composition emphasizes the vastness of the night sky and the serene beauty of the natural landscape.",
